&lt;!-- /wp:heading --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Traditional marketing playbooks of the past are no longer working. The infusion of AI didn't just speed marketing up but collapsed the distance between strategy and execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The marketing leaders who win aren't the ones with the best frameworks. They're the ones who've learned to train systems, meet modern customer expectations, and deliver real-time outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Led by Marc Sirkin (former CEO, Third Door Media; advisor to CMOs navigating GTM resets), this session shows you how to build marketing strategy that actually delivers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You'll learn:&lt;br&gt;&gt; Why the old strategy playbook is broken (and what comes next)&lt;br&gt;&gt; The new operating model: From plans to trained systems&lt;br&gt;&gt; The SPOT → BUILD → TEST → SCALE framework in action&lt;br&gt;&gt; Real examples: Sales enablement, content, GTM execution&lt;br&gt;&gt; How to start training your systems&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Online | April 21, 2026 | 10:00 a.m. - 12:00 p.m. Central Time&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
