&lt;!-- /wp:heading --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:list --&gt;
&lt;ul class=\&quot;wp-block-list\&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- wp:list-item --&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why marketing strategy fails to execute&lt;/strong&gt;. Diagnose the real gap between strategy and delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:list-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:list-item --&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The new operating system for marketing execution&lt;/strong&gt;. How modern marketing teams collapse the distance between strategy and results using the SPOT → BUILD → TEST → SCALE framework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:list-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:list-item --&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How AI changes what execution means&lt;/strong&gt;. Where AI actually moves the needle vs. where it creates noise (and how to tell the difference)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:list-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:list-item --&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to design and deliver pilots that deliver&lt;/strong&gt;. Build focused experiments that produce measurable outcomes in 30-60 days without organizational drama&lt;/li&gt;
