&lt;h3 class=\&quot;wp-block-heading is-style-default\&quot; id=\&quot;h-11-modules\&quot;&gt;11 Modules&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:heading --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 1: Meet the Instructor\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start the course off by learning a little about the instructor and setting the stage for what you will learn in the course.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 2: What Is Data and Analytics\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lay the foundation with a baseline understanding of what data and analytics can provide and how they can be used.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 3: Analytics Process\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Begin your data journey by determining your goals and understanding the data analytics life cycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

