&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 5: Importance of Data Analytics\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Level set why it is important to focus on data and analytics given the huge investment of time and energy to do it right.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 6: Marketing \u0026amp; Advertising Metrics\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take a look at the most common marketing and advertising metrics and when you might focus on them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 7: Channels and Types of Data\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gain an understanding of the different channels and tools where you might gather the various different metrics and the types of data you might get.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 8: Business Intelligence Platforms\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Review some of the top business intelligence platforms to determine which tools can help you quickly access and analyze your data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 9: Data Visualizations\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Look at data differently by using charts, graphs or infographics to visualize trends and gaps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 10: Dashboards\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Focus on how to see the bigger picture and share access with others by setting up dashboards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;

&lt;!-- wp:ama/accordion-item {\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Module 11: What's Next\&quot;} --&gt;
&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Complete the course by taking an ungraded Knowledge Check and reviewing additional opportunities to continue learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion-item --&gt;
&lt;!-- /wp:ama/accordion --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
